ZH: 我想去海边度假。
EN: I want to go on vacation by the sea.

ZH: 明天我们一起去海里游泳吧。
EN: Let's go swimming in the sea together tomorrow.

ZH: 海水很清澈。
EN: The sea water is very clear.

ZH: 在沙滩上看日出是我最喜欢的事情。
EN: Watching the sunrise on the beach is my favorite thing to do.

ZH: 海浪冲得很高。
EN: The waves in the sea are crashing high.

ZH: 坐在海边，能听到潮水声。
EN: Sitting by the sea, you can hear the sound of the waves.

ZH: 我去夏威夷看海龟。
EN: I went to Hawaii to see sea turtles.

ZH: 海风吹得很凉爽。
EN: The sea breeze blows cool.

ZH: 海鲜是我最爱吃的食物。
EN: Seafood is my favorite food to eat.

ZH: 为了拯救海洋生物，我们要减少使用塑料袋。
EN: To save marine life, we must reduce the use of plastic bags.

ZH: 海洋是地球上最大的自然资源。
EN: The ocean is the Earth's largest natural resource.

ZH: 她身穿白色连衣裙漫步在海滩上。
EN: She walks along the beach in a white dress.

ZH: 海豚是海洋的灵魂。
EN: Dolphins are the soul of the sea.

ZH: 海洋的生命非常丰富。
EN: The marine life is very abundant.

ZH: 来自海外的孩子们在沙滩上玩耍。
EN: Children from overseas play on the beach.

ZH: 海水太凉了，我不想下去。
EN: The sea water is too cold, I don't want to go in.

ZH: 海浪滚滚，仿佛在吟诵着一首歌。
EN: The rolling waves seem to be singing a song.

ZH: 每年，我们都去海边度假。
EN: Every year, we go on vacation by the sea.

ZH: 海域被污染了，许多生物受到了影响。
EN: The sea has been polluted, and many organisms are affected.

ZH: 他在海边捡到了一只美丽的贝壳。
EN: He found a beautiful seashell on the beach.
